613
00:38:47.700 --> 00:38:52.499
<i>Aku ingin berwarna di wajahmu...</i>

614
00:38:54.970 --> 00:38:58.409
<i>Sebagaimana malam yang memerah...</i>

615
00:38:58.639 --> 00:39:01.280
<i>Atau ketika mentari terbenam...</i>

616
00:39:01.880 --> 00:39:06.650
<i>Aku ingin berwarna di pipimu...</i>

617
00:39:09.349 --> 00:39:13.959
<i>Jika aku seorang pujangga...</i>

618
00:39:16.619 --> 00:39:20.499
